# Changelog

## [m3-rf-globe] — 2026-04-05

### M3 — RF → Globe integration
- sentinel-core: auth, bus bridge, reverse proxy, health aggregator
- End-to-end: local SDR feed → Redis → WebSocket → CesiumJS globe
- 51 tests passing

### M2 — Globe layer
- CesiumJS globe with Google Photorealistic 3D Tiles
- AircraftLayer, VesselLayer, SatelliteLayer (CelesTrak TLE + SGP4)
- PostFx shaders: NVG, FLIR, CRT
- ControlPanel, CameraPresets, AlertDrawer, InfoPanel
- Dev mock feed with VITE_NO_MOCK=1 escape hatch

### M1 — RF pipeline  
- ADSBDecoder poll-based with live and mock replay modes
- RFPublisher with GPS enrichment
- Flask-SocketIO app, health endpoint

### M0 — Foundation
- sentinel-common: EventEnvelope, EventKind, BusPublisher, BusConsumer, geo utils
- Redis Streams event bus
- Docker Compose baseline